Alot has happened since last time I wrote in here..i mean ALOT..i havent written in here since like May 15th..or something? but ill just start with the memorial day weekend.Well on Friday(May 27)i left form school early because i was going to the beach for memorial day weekend with rachael!We went to Hilton Head..and we stayed at this Disney Resort..we went from Friday-Sunday!we got so burn/tan!:D..well it was lots of fun!we have to do it again sometime!Anyways now about school.
we only have like 2 and a half more days of school!:),its good and bad..becase this year i have become so close to 2 people and im sad that we are all gonna go our separate ways to different high schools..i mean i hope we stay in touch and stuff!:D..and its good that school is over becuase i get to go to South America!June 8th.(a day after school is over).and im not coming back until the 6th of July..then i MIGHT go to the beach for like a week with Hannah's family!:D.so im happy about that!well tommorow we get yearbooks and its yearbook signing as well!then afterschool is the "Jamaican Jam"..form 3:30-5:30.im staying afterschool..then maybe at night i might be going to the lake for the weekend..it all depeneds on the weather..but yea..i hope i can go, becuase i havent gone in such a long time and i wanna ride on the wave runner! Well changing the subject..today i found out that i got a 94 on my Algebra EOC!yay!i was so happy..and i found out some of my grades as well..they werent that great but i guess they were kind of good!:D.Well tommorow is Aneesa's little party thing and i dont know if im gonna go becuase i still havent asked my mom!but yea.i gotta think about what im doing tommorow.but ok..im gonna go now..ill talk to you kids laterr. <Marquee>Erika

<Marquee>Ahh!Sorry!</Marquee>
i know i havent updated in a while.I will before I leave to South America!Im so freaking sad that middle school is almost over,and we are all going to go to different schools.:(.well atleast i am..i really dont wanna.well ill update later..if i fell like it!xoxo. <Marquee>Erika .

I havent REALLY updated since..i dont remember when..although i did a survey last night thats not really updating cause well it just isnt!anyways ill start from friday:
FRIDAY:
Went to school.Afterschool went home with Rachel Goldstein becuase she was havin a party at her hosue.It all started as a little "get-together" then turned into a party!It was soo much fun!i hadnt had that much fun since..Jasmine's party!There was alot of people there!here are some that i can remember:
Me!
Rachel Goldstein
Rachael Shulga
Rachel Graham
Hannah
Sophia
Jasmine
Aneessa
Tati
Brooke Bentley
Tyler Flack
Liam
Jack
Ozzie
Chris
Candace
Justin
and i think that was it?
We all went swimmin in the pool, then it got cold and we all went in the hot tub!about 15 people in like a 5 people hot tub!:)!HERPES!haha!the hot tub was so much fun!until it started to get cold!then it sucked!me and tati were the last ones out!:)!<3
Well yeah then aroun 11 or so everyone left, and we had to go drop off Liam..me,rachael,sophia,hannah,candace and tati all slept @ rachel's!we had a very exhausted night so we fell asleep watching "Summer Catch" i wantched like the first minute and fell asleep!and that was my friday night!
SATURDAY
Woke up to the sound of Hannah's cellphone..and it was no other than RICKY!like always having to call early!:(..so we all woke up to that..then we just hung out for like an hour.then we were hungry so we went to Chick-Fil-A for breakfeast..we went through the drive thru because we were in our PJ's, then we went back to rachel's, ate out by the pool, cleaned up a lil bit then i threw my cousin in the pool, and then they pushed me in and we all just ended up swimming in our PJ's and in the hot tub!Then at like 12:30 we had to leave cause rachel mom's had to go to a lunch with her family so we got dropped off at tati's house, from there we walked to Providence Court!It wasnt really fun because the AlKurd's couldnt come down, so we were talking to them from the balcony!then we went back to Tati's,had some milkshakes,went on the computer,later the AlKurd's came over!then we left at around 5:30? we went to Hannah's hosue to get ready for the movies..got ready and rachel came and picked us up..i went to the movies with da "Crew",instead of going to Kendall's surprise party@:)we watched "House Of Wax" which sucked!it only got one-star!it was reallyy bad! "This town is so freaky-looking"..afterwards we walked to Micky D's and then Tati took us home!then i got dropped off at my house and went to sleep!*Night Night*
SUNDAY
Happy Mother's Day!We woke up early and went for breakfeast to Panera Bread!i <3 that place!then we came back home and stayed here until 5..then we went to Barolo for Mother's day dinner!that was good too! then we wen to Hannah's hosue cause our family was there, we stayed there until like 11?then we came back home, i studied for the DBQ and went to sleep!
MONDAY
Went to school.had the DBQ..it was really confusing!it sucked!well then i went home..i ate..and i watched TV..then i made my little niece go to sleep!now im here really bored getting ready to go do my homework..o and im getting ready to buy my tickets for the summer!im going to South America from June 8th to July 6th or something like that?!HECK YES!:)!well i will miss you all!<3 e a c
laterr kidds!

So i havent updated since Thursday,i really cant remember alot since then,but ill try.
Thursday:
Afterschool i went home,then around 6 i went over to Hannah's house cause i was gonna sleep there sicne we didnt have school on friday!yes!so i went and only hannahs sister was there so i was there with her and we were bored and so we waited until her mom came and she finally got there with rachael and had *Starbucks*for us!:)!like an hour later we went to bed bath and beyond and looked at some stuff..then went to pick up hannah from my cousins house then came back home and fell asleep!*Night Night*
Friday:
I woke up around 11:30 and then around 1:10 my mom came and got me from hannah's house because she wanted to take me and my brother out to lunch!so we went to this place called "Panera Bread" it was really good!!my aunt and hannahs family came and joined us after a little while!so that was fun we were there for like 2 hours talking about everyone!haha!then i went with hannah's mom and we went to Target to get a present for my cousin then we went home to pick up Jasmine cause her mom had dropped her off at hannah's hosue so we were there for like 1 hour then ater that we dropped off my cousin @ a party and we went to southpark mall!i got some really cute stuff!:)!i got an outfitt from abercrombie!and i also got some pants from urban outfitters! so then hannah's dad called and said to go to *Texas Roadhouse* becasue we were gonna eat there for dinner!it was really yummy!:)..so around 7:30 we went home and then went to the movies with PART of our crew cause the others were at the beach!the movies was so much fun unitl someone decieded that they neede to ruin it!(not naming any names!)so Hannah was being really loud and this lady was like "will you shut the hell up or im gonna go call the manager"so me and rachael didnt wanna get kicked out so we decided we should go walk around..we were leaving and ozzie was like ill go with you so he came with us to McDonald's and then George came and he came with us too.anyways we were there for like an hour then everyone came from the movies at like 11.then hannah's mom was coming to pick us up so we had to run back to the movies!after she came we went home watched *Making The Band 3* and fell asleep!:)!
Saturday:
I woke up around 12:30 and my mom called saying she was coming to pick me up because we were going to the mall!so i got ready and left..i went to Carolina Place Mall..i went to hollister and got an outfitt from there!and i got the perfume!ahh i love the smell of it!:)!Perfume=Love!so then my mom was in a store named *Kirkland's* for like an hour becuase she was looking for stuff for the house so i was reallyy bored so i went and walked around with my cousin and saw Tabitha and Darcy going down the stairs!then we saw our aunt and we went with her because she had to go home becuase she didnt have her purse..so we went and got her purse but never went back to the mall..we went to eat @ *Ice Cream And Pizza Works*it was very good!:)!after we went to hannahs house and we all slept there because she left us there because she was going out!
Sunday:
Woke up around 12:30 and was at hannah's house unitl like 3:45,my aunt decided we should go somewhere.so me,rachael,and my aunt went out.i got dropped off at the salon and got my roots done!and my aunt came later to get me then we went to pick up rachael because she was getting her facial done!then we went to the grocery store and got some stuff for the family cookout we were gonna have!went home.cooked.and left at like 10.went home changed into my PJ's.went to sleep!
Monday:!
I went to school.It wasnt really that great!it was pretty boring!nothing really happened!then around 6 i took a little nap and woke up around 7:30..hopefully i will be able to go to sleep tonight!:/.well thats pretty much my weekend including monday!boring huh?well i have to go do my homework so im gonna have to BOUNCE!
laterr kiddos!

Since i dont have anything else to do i decided that i should update my livejournal!Anyways today i went on  fieldtrip to the Levin Museum of the New South or whatever its called!i had an awesome time with kristi and jenna and our awesome instructor Ernest Mobley!he was so cool!well we were there since like 9:45 till like 12:30 or so? then we came back to school and ate lunch..being the nice teacher mrs.miller is (yea right) she decided that we should invite Mr.Chevy's and Mrs.Wright's class to our class to eat lunch together!it was very fun!i ate lunch with kristi,jenna,darcy,kimmy,kristen,kendall,jenna b,and rachel(didnt talk) but that was it!so then @ around 1:40 we finished and had to go to our last period class..i had Chevy! we didnt really do anyithing except for these charts but it was so much fun becuase i was with jenna b and kaitlyn and they were making me laguh so hard!:)! So after school my mom picked me up and then we went to harris teeter to get some food and then we came home and ate!mm! after i was finished i came upstairs and watched TV..i fell slept for like 2 hrs casue i was reallyyy tired!school wore me out today!hopefully i will be able to sleep tonight since i slept like practically ALL afternoon! well right now i am really bored so i am watching American Idol and i might be going to blockbuster and maggie moo's later!:).. well im gonna go now maybe ill write some more later if i feel like it!:)comment!

So..I havent updated in a LONG TIME! but..anyways,i dont remember anything that has happened over the past weeks/weekend. Except for yesterday afterschool i had to stay for math and make up a test that i did REALLY bad on! but i did better when i retook it! and so when i was leaving the talent show was on, so i watched like 3 people perform and they werent realyl good.. so then my mom came and picked me up and after that i went home and then i had to go to see some of my stepdad's family from Maine, but it was supposed to be a "dinner" but they didnt really have any food there, except for salad, so after we left there we were all really hungry and went to eat @ this new resaturant named "Red Robin" @ like 9:30, the food was really good there. There was alot of like teenagers working there, so i asked how old you had to be to work there and they were like 14, so i wanted to work there but then they told me you had to be 15, so yea..even if i was 15 i wouldnt be able to work because i wont be here for like the WHOLE summer..casue like 2 days after school ends im going to SOUTH AMERICA for a month!(YES!)and after i come back im going to the beach for like a month with hannah's family!(YES!)hopefully i will come back like BLACK!lol! anyways,right now im at hannah's house and im with hannah,rachael,sophia,lainey and scarlet.and we were having fun like a minute ago but were bored now!so yea, i decided to update, but anyways.. i dont know what im doing this weekend,i will mayb go to see children of eden! i cant wait to see it! its gonna be so cool! JENNA I HOPE YOU DID GOOD TONIGHT!CANT WAIT TO SEE YOU! So,gonna go cause im really bored and dont really have anything else to say!COMMENT!

YES THANKS TO KRISTEN NOW I HAVE PRETTIFUL LIVEJOURNAL!thanks kristen!i love you!anyways,nothing realy exciting happened this week.. I've been really sick these past days! it really suck because i keep sneezing and my throat really hurts and yeah its just not fun!anyways... yesterday i went shopping with hannah and my cousins.. that was fun!then i went out to dinner with the family to Won Fu!i love that restaurant. after that we went to celebration station and had a wonderful time riding the Go Karts! that was so much fun.. then we went back in and got some tokens and played some more. i got 260 tickets so i went to rade them in but instead i gave all of them to my little 6 year old cousin..once we were getting ready to leave we saw this group of like 10 kids that were all gothic and they were pretty discusting! they were kissing each other.. i think they were like lesbians or something. very disturbing!then this girl likle pulled her shirt up and the other girl was giving her a hicky in her stomach! which was disturbing to see.! so we left aroun 11:30 or so? then i slept over hannah's house again for the second time and when we got home we were pretty tired so we watched TV for a little while then we went to sleep. and this morning they brought me back to my house around 11:45 because i had to go to church @ 12:30 so i went to Church after  that i came back home and now im here.. bored out of my mind! talking with the parents about going to Hawaii with my cousins for SB!they said yes but now we just have to find some tickets.!hopefully i have luck and there is still some left!:)! wish me luck in trying to find some! well im gonna go now because i really dont have anything else to say!
